# Tefter.bg License

## License Selection Guide

The licensing options include the Community MIT license (free) and Commercial License (not free).

### License Equality
We are committed to provide all users with the full power of our platform, regardless of the license they select. Whether you choose our Community MIT license or opt for the Commercial license, you'll enjoy the same extensive set of features:
- Complete access to all Tefter.bg functionalities.
- Support for commercial applications and use cases.
- Flexibility to create, sell and deploy your own closed-source add-on providers, applications or complete solutions.

### Transitive Dependency Usе
If you're using Tefter.bg in general or the libraries that are part of it as a transitive dependency, same license conditions apply as it is general use.

### Non-profit Usе
If you represent a charitable organization or are using Tefter.bg for educational purposes or training courses, you can also access it for free under the Community MIT license.

### Small Businesses
For companies with annual gross revenue below $1 million USD, Tefter.bg is available for free under the Community MIT license.

### Larger Businesses
Companies with annual gross revenue exceeding $1 million USD must purchase a paid Commercial license.

### Beyond Compliance
Purchasing a license is not just about following our guidelines; it's also an opportunity to support the ongoing development of Tefter.bg. Your contribution enables us to enhance the library and provide exceptional support to all users.

